{"tid":1969884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台撚緊食衞局 問許冠傑演唱會係咪違反左限聚令","createTime":"2020-04-12T17:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T01:42:37.000Z","uid":5195,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c590125f6e1141e9b43a7a333fb3a2a15e2e3a02","tid":1969884,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T17:37:51.000Z","msg":"食衞局：豁免是否適用製作單位須視乎當時情況<br />\n2020-04-12 HKT 23:10<br />\n<br />\n歌手許冠傑下午在尖沙咀一個商場天台，以網上直播形式舉行演唱會，製作團隊超過4人。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局表示，禁止人群聚集的規例下列明，「在工作地點為工作而進行的群組聚集」可獲豁免，不過在評估時須考慮所有適當及相關因素。<br />\n<br />\n食衞局回覆本台查詢時說，豁免是否適用於演唱會製作單位拍攝節目，須視乎當時的實際情況及工作性質，例如公眾人士能否進入該地點，參與人士是否有工作指示，聚集發生的一刻是「為工作而進行」等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520290-20200412.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520290-20200412.htm&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=fb779988\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520290-20200412.htm&h=280b0a94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520290-20200412.htm</a>"},{"pid":"797c072afa9221075640572a78a5bbc8520f309e","tid":1969884,"uid":12510,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T17:42:51.000Z","msg":"咁講酒吧落閘開會都係工作喇"},{"pid":"0bbff9f7fe2d61ba787199d96a4524519295e94e","tid":1969884,"uid":59976,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T17:45:31.000Z","msg":"一早都話個show係政府有份搞黎維穩架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5898288063d48f622fc3254e5312574198b744a2","tid":1969884,"uid":312526,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T17:47:19.000Z","msg":"酒吧開會唔係工作？？"},{"pid":"800c9d7e4f8c7c7e58cff3ca8b7c9cf44c56dc0e","tid":1969884,"uid":59976,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T17:49:02.000Z","msg":"只要林鄭開心，犯法又有咩所謂喎，許同志好野<img src=\"/assets/fac